        Creates new item with respective parameters
        Parameters:
        name - Name of the item
        url - String to find location of image data
        desc - String to describe the object
        cost - int for how muh item cost
        owner - user that has the item
        location - Location of the item
        type - Type of the item
        effectType - Effect type of the item
        effect - Effect of the item
